Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:38.87,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梳大背頭的亮士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.41,0:22:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮士!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:42.12,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是讓人耳目一新
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 交給我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道喚醒公主的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:52.99,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 就這麼讓他吻下去嗎大神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:11.25,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來大神的腦子哪裡壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了涼子?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子 赤井
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:25.39,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太不講道理啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是煩惱多多的青春花季啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦...
